WEBVTT

00:02:59.302 --> 00:03:01.201
Katika umri wa miaka minne,

00:03:01.225 --> 00:03:03.172
zaidi ya asilimia 80 hudanganya.

00:03:04.334 --> 00:03:06.785
Na baada ya miaka minne,

00:03:06.809 --> 00:03:08.198
watoto wengi hudanganya.

00:03:09.180 --> 00:03:10.543
Hivyo unaweza kuona,

00:03:10.567 --> 00:03:14.030
kudanganya ni sehemu halisi
ya kuendelea.

00:03:14.054 --> 00:03:16.844
Na baadhi ya watoto huanza kusema uwongo

00:03:16.868 --> 00:03:19.307
wakiwa na umri mdogo wa miaka miwili.

00:03:20.438 --> 00:03:23.995
Hivyo sasa, tuangalie kwa ukaribu
watoto wadogo.

00:03:25.336 --> 00:03:29.149
Kwanini baadhi na sio wote
watoto wadogo hudanganya?